*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZPRO_CONDENSE_STATEMENT_641
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zpro_condense_statement_641.

DATA : lv_text(50) TYPE c VALUE'       Leading Spaces along with text'.

WRITE : 'Text before condense:',lv_text.

SKIP 2.
CONDENSE lv_text.
WRITE : 'Text after condense:',lv_text.

SKIP 2.
CONDENSE lv_text NO-GAPS.
WRITE : 'Text after condense with NO GAP  :',lv_text.
